## Prohibited

### Code

- ❌ `any` type — Use `unknown` or specific types
- ❌ `console.log` — Use the `logger` utility
- ❌ Inline styles — Use Tailwind classes
- ❌ Magic numbers — Define constants
- ❌ Non-null assertions (`!`) — Handle null explicitly
- ❌ String interpolation in SQL — Use parameterized queries
- ❌ Default exports — Use named exports

### Git

- ❌ Secrets in code — Use environment variables
- ❌ Force pushes — Use PRs
- ❌ Commit directly to main — Code review required
- ❌ Large files in git — Use Git LFS > 5MB

### Dependencies

- ❌ Unaudited packages — Run `npm audit` first
- ❌ Outdated major versions — Keep current
- ❌ Unused imports — Remove immediately

