## Commit Conventions

### Format

```
<type>(<scope>): <description>

[optional body]

[optional footer]
```

### Types

| Type | Description |
|------|-------------|
| feat | New feature |
| fix | Bug fix |
| docs | Documentation |
| style | Formatting (no logic) |
| refactor | Code restructure |
| test | Tests |
| chore | Tooling, dependencies |

### Examples

```
feat(auth): implement OAuth2 flow

- Add Google provider
- Handle token refresh
- Store tokens in HttpOnly cookies

Closes #123
```

```
fix(dashboard): correct chart rendering on resize

Charts weren't updating when container size changed.
Added ResizeObserver to trigger re-render.

Fixes #456
```

